20Mattress%20Protector%20was%20the%20strong%20initial%20odor%20it%20had%20out%20of%20the%20box.%20Fortunately%2C%20it%20dissipated%20by%20bedtime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20budget%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221165%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Saferest%20premium%20mattress%20protector%20on%20a%20bed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63c991d3eee94d001a78fdc1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22874%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20budget-friendly%20SafeRest%20Premium%20Mattress%20Protector%20fits%20mattresses%20up%20to%2018%20inches%20thick.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20tested%20four%20mattress%20protectors%20that%20cost%20less%20than%20%2430.%20Of%20those%2C%20the%20SafeRest%20Premium%20Mattress%20Protector%20performed%20the%20best.%20In%20addition%20to%20remaining%20leak-free%20in%20our%20tests%2C%20it%20was%20one%20of%20the%20best%20at%20staying%20cool%20and%20dissipating%20heat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20SafeRest%20protector%20can%20fit%20a%20broad%20range%20of%20mattresses%20up%20to%2018%20inches%20thick.%20As%20with%20many%20protectors%2C%20the%20part%20that%20rests%20on%20top%20of%20your%20mattress%20is%20made%20of%20a%20different%20material%20than%20the%20skirt%20around%20the%20sides.%20The%20top%20is%20waterproof%2C%20while%20the%20sides%20are%20not.%20Fortunately%2C%20the%20top%20fit%20my%20mattress%20well%20and%20covered%20it%20to%20the%20edges%2C%20even%20after%20putting%20it%20through%20the%20washer%20and%20dryer%20five%20times.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20surface%20is%20terry%20cloth%20and%20not%20the%20most%20comfortable.%20As%20I%20moved%20in%20the%20night%2C%20it%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20crackling%20noises%2C%20and%20my%20fitted%20sheet%20didn't%20shift%20smoothly%20on%20it.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20a%20solid%20budget%20option%20that%20didn't%20ruin%20my%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20cooling%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Helix%20Mattress%20Protector%20is%20on%20a%20bed%20while%20a%20child%20lays%20on%20top%20of%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63c992012a1e600018b8c157%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Helix%20Mattress%20Protector%20allows%20your%20mattress%20to%20breathe%2C%20so%20you%20don't%20overheat%20at%20night.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20researching%20this%20guide%2C%20one%20of%20the%20complaints%20I%20heard%20about%20mattress%20protectors%20is%20that%20they%20can%20trap%20heat%20and%20cause%20sleepers%20to%20overheat.%20So%2C%20I%20looked%20at%20how%20hot%20the%20mattress%20protectors%20got%20after%20sleeping%20on%20them%20and%20how%20quickly%20the%20heat%20dissipated.%20The%20Helix%20Mattress%20Protector%20was%20one%20of%20the%20best%20at%20staying%20cool%20and%20dissipating%20heat%20fast.%20In%20fact%2C%20within%20two%20minutes%20of%20getting%20up%20from%20the%20bed%2C%20the%20surface%20temperature%20plunged%20more%20than%2014%20degrees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20our%20evaluations%2C%20the%20Helix%20passed%20the%20leakage%20tests%20with%20flying%20colors%20before%20and%20after%20putting%20it%20through%20five%20washing%20and%20drying%20cycles.%20The%20protector%20also%20didn't%20show%20any%20shrinkage%20after%20the%20washings%2C%20which%20is%20essential%20since%20the%20waterproof%20TPU%20backing%20is%20only%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20protector%20that%20covers%20the%20mattress%20top%20and%20not%20on%20the%20skirting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20its%20soft%20surface%2C%20the%20protector%20was%20comfortable%20to%20sleep%20on.%20I%20tend%20to%20overheat%20at%20night%20but%20didn't%20experience%20any%20issues.%20It%20was%20also%20one%20of%20the%20quietest%20protectors%3B%20I%20didn't%20notice%20any%20crackling%20or%20rustling%20as%20I%20shifted%20in%20the%20night.%20At%20100%20nights%2C%20the%20Helix%20protector%20has%20one%20of%20the%20longest%20trial%20periods%20of%20any%20of%20the%20models%20we%20tested%2C%20but%20it%20also%20has%20one%20of%20the%20shortest%20warranties%20%E2%80%94%20just%20one%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20mattress%20encasement%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221727%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Utopia%20zippered%20mattress%20encasement%20on%20a%20bed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63c99224eee94d001a78fdde%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221295%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Utopia%20Bedding%20Zippered%20Mattress%20Encasement%20covers%20your%20mattress%20completely%2C%20keeping%20all%20sides%20safe%20from%20liquids%20and%20bed%20bugs.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBed%20bugs%20can%20cost%20hundreds%20to%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20to%20get%20rid%20of%2C%20and%20even%20then%2C%20there's%20no%20guarantee%20they%20won't%20come%20back.%20So%20it's%20worth%20the%20%2430%20investment%20to%20cover%20your%20mattress%20with%20a%20full%20encasement.%20The%20best%20encasement%20I%20tested%20is%20the%20Utopia%20Bedding%20Zippered%20Mattress%20Encasement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20passed%20the%20leakage%20tests%20before%20and%20after%20washing%2C%20and%20most%20of%20the%20liquid%20pooled%20on%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20encasement.%20It%20was%20one%20of%20the%20quietest%20protectors%20and%20never%20got%20hot%20when%20I%20slept%20on%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20significant%20pain%20with%20any%20encasement%20is%20putting%20it%20on.%20Fortunately%2C%20the%20Utopia%20Bedding%20encasement%20has%20a%20wide%20zippered%20opening%20that%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20slide%20over%20your%20mattress%20as%20you%20hold%20it%20up%20vertically.%20Once%20zipped%2C%20a%20Velcro%20flap%20keeps%20the%20slider%20body%20and%20pull%20tab%20in%20place%20and%20ensures%20there%20aren't%20any%20holes%20for%20bed%20bugs%20to%20sneak%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20encasement%20was%20comfortable%20to%20sleep%20on.%20The%20thin%20material%20was%20barely%20noticeable%20under%20the%20fitted%20sheet.%20The%20only%20major%20downside%20is%20that%20it%20doesn't%20come%20with%20a%20warranty.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20it's%20worth%20noting%20that%20no%20encasement%20protects%20you%20from%20getting%20bed%20bugs.%20Instead%2C%20it%20protects%20your%20mattress%2C%20an%20expensive%20investment%2C%20from%20harboring%20bed%20bugs%20that%20can%20destroy%20it%20over%20time.%20If%20a%20mattress%20is%20already%20riddled%20with%20bed%20bugs%2C%20an%20encasement%20can%20trap%20them.%20But%20you%20need%20to%20keep%20it%20on%20for%20at%20least%2012%20months%20to%20kill%20all%20the%20bugs%2C%20and%20you'll%20still%20need%20to%20treat%20your%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20deep%20pocket%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20lucid%20mattress%20protector%20out%20of%20the%20package.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61f46b7d45edd800183b4289%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Lucid%20Waterproof%20Mattress%20Protector%20is%20great%20for%20mattresses%20up%20to%2022%20inches%20thick.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20mattress%20protector%20doesn't%20do%20you%20any%20good%20if%20it%20doesn't%20stay%20on.%20Those%20with%20thicker%20mattresses%20may%20have%20found%20difficulty%20finding%20one%20that%20properly%20fits.%20Enter%20the%20Lucid%20Terry%20Top%20Mattress%20Protector.%20It%20features%20deep%20pockets%20that%20fit%20beds%20up%20to%2022%20inches%20thick%2C%20the%20thickest%20protector%20we%20tested.%20This%20is%20a%20plus%20when%20you%20have%20a%20mattress%20topper%20that%20increases%20the%20thickness%20of%20your%20bed%20and%20needs%20protection%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20its%20budget%20sub-%2425%20price%2C%20the%20Lucid%20mattress%20protector%20passed%20our%20leakage%20tests%20with%20flying%20colors%2C%20even%20after%20five%20washings.%20Liquid%20pools%20on%20the%20surface%20rather%20than%20absorbing%20into%20the%20fabric.%20It's%20also%20backed%20by%20the%20longest%20warranty%20of%20our%20picks%3A%2015%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20at%20this%20price%20point%2C%20there%20are%20always%20negatives.%20Specifically%2C%20this%20was%20one%20of%20the%20noisest%20protectors%20in%20our%20tests.%20There's%20a%20noticeable%20crinkling%20sound%20as%20you%20shift%20positions.%20It%20also%20seemed%20to%20trap%20heat%2C%20though%20it%20was%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20pack%20comfort-wise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20negatives%2C%20the%20Lucid%20Terry%20Top%20is%20what%20I%20purchased%20to%20protect%20the%20pricier%20mattresses%20in%20my%20home.%20My%20top%20considerations%20are%20a%20budget%20price%2C%20ease%20of%20use%2C%20and%20protection%20from%20spills.%20The%20Lucid%20has%20served%20me%20well%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECheck%20out%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Flucid-mattress-protector-review%5C%22%3ELucid%20Mattress%20Protector%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20waterproof%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tuft%20%26amp%3B%20Needle%20mattress%20protector%20on%20a%20bed%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a17a716979d7371822e6f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Tuft%20%26amp%3B%20Needle%20Mattress%20Protector%20didn't%20let%20any%20liquid%20through%2C%20even%20after%20several%20trips%20through%20the%20washer%20and%20dryer.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20liquids%20can%20so%20easily%20destroy%20a%20mattress%2C%20waterproofing%20is%20a%20requirement%20for%20inclusion%20in%20this%20guide.%20While%20all%20our%20picks%20are%20waterproof%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20draw%20special%20attention%20to%20the%20Tuft%20%26amp%3B%20Needle%20Mattress%20Protector%20because%20it%20excelled%20at%20keeping%20liquids%20from%20passing%20through%2C%20even%20after%20five%20washing%20and%20drying%20cycles.%20I%20also%20liked%20that%20the%20protector%20absorbed%20much%20of%20the%20liquid%2C%20keeping%20some%20of%20it%20from%20getting%20on%20your%20bedding%2C%20the%20floor%2C%20or%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20protector%20meets%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oeko-tex.com%2Fen%2Fapply-here%2Foeko-tex-standard-100%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOEKO-TEX%3C%2Fa%3E%20standards%2C%20meaning%20it's%20free%20from%20harmful%20chemicals%20and%20substances.%20It%20offers%20waterproof%20protection%20along%20the%20sides%20of%20the%20mattress%2C%20too.%C2%A0%20I%20found%20the%20soft%20top%20of%20the%20protector%20was%20comfortable%20to%20sleep%20on%20and%20made%20minimal%20noise%20as%20I%20shifted%20positions.%20However%2C%20it%20trapped%20heat%20in%20my%20temperature%20tests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tuft%20%26amp%3B%20Needle%20Mattress%20Protector%20doesn't%20come%20with%20head%2Ffoot%20labels%20to%20help%20you%20orient%20it%20as%20you%20put%20it%20on%2C%20and%20it%20only%20fits%20mattresses%20up%20to%2014%20inches%20thick.%20Yet%2C%20I%20had%20no%20trouble%20installing%20it%20on%20appropriately%20sized%20mattresses%2C%20and%20I%20found%20it%20stayed%20in%20place%20without%20bunching%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20this%20protector%20has%20the%20longest%20home%20trial%20period%20of%20any%20model%20I%20tested%20at%20100%20nights%20when%20purchased%20directly%20from%20Tuft%20%26amp%3B%20Needle.%20If%20you%20don't%20like%20it%2C%20you%20can%20return%20it%20for%20free%20with%20a%20full%20refund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20tested%20each%20mattress%20protector%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Every%20mattress%20protector%20tested%20for%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20best%20mattress%20protectors%2C%20with%20blue%20water%20on%20each%20to%20measure%20water%20protection.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F608b2abc35c46f0018c0b5d0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20tested%20to%20see%20if%20the%20mattress%20protectors%20were%20waterproof%20before%20and%20after%20washing%20them%20five%20times.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20personally%20tested%20all%20of%20the%20mattress%20protectors%20in%20this%20guide.%20In%20addition%20to%20sleeping%20on%20each%20protector%2C%20there%20are%20many%20objective%20tests%20each%20model%20goes%20through.%20The%20most%20important%20factors%20to%20consider%20when%20choosing%20a%20mattress%20protector%20are%20comfort%2C%20protection%2C%20and%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHere%20are%20some%20of%20the%20test%20results%20for%20the%20main%20attributes%20we%20tested%3A%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Ctable%20border%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EAttribute%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3EPurple%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3ESafeRest%20Premium%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3EHelix%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3EUtopia%20Bedding%20Encasement%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3ELucid%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3ETuft%20%26amp%3B%20Needle%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EComfort%20score%20(1%20uncomfortable%20to%205%20comfortable)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E5%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E3.5%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E4%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E4%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E4%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E4%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EProtects%20against%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3ELiquid%20and%20dust%20mites%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3ELiquid%20and%20dust%20mites%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3ELiquid%20and%20dust%20mites%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3ELiquid%2C%20bed%20bugs%2C%20and%20dust%20mites%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3ELiquid%20and%20dust%20mites%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3ELiquid%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EMattress%20thicknesses%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3EUp%20to%2015%20inches%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3EUp%20to%2018%20inches%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3EUp%20to%2015%20inches%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3EUp%20to%2015%