id%20Derek%20Hales%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20mattress%20review%20site%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnaplab.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENapLab%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20softer-than-average%20mattress%20will%20let%20side%20sleepers%20sink%20in%2C%20helping%20them%20achieve%20spinal%20alignment.%20Zoned%20support%20is%20also%20helpful%20for%20side%20sleepers%20who%20need%20increased%20pressure-point%20relief%20to%20keep%20their%20spine%20aligned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBack%20sleepers%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBack%20sleepers%20don't%20want%20to%20sink%20in%20as%20much%20as%20side%20sleepers%2C%20so%20a%20medium-firm%20mattress%20is%20better.%20When%20you're%20lying%20flat%2C%20it%20will%20keep%20your%20back%20closer%20to%20neutral.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStomach%20sleepers%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGoetting%20said%20a%20firm%20mattress%20is%20important%20because%20stomach%20sleepers%20must%20rotate%20their%20head%20to%20breathe%2C%20leaving%20the%20spine%20out%20of%20alignment.%20When%20you%20couple%20this%20with%20a%20pillow%20that%20causes%20your%20head%20to%20flex%20backward%2C%20you're%20more%20prone%20to%20restless%20sleep%20and%20neck%20pain.%20A%20firm%20mattress%20reduces%20the%20degree%20to%20which%20your%20head%20flexes%20backward.%20In%20general%2C%20the%20experts%20I've%20talked%20to%20recommend%20avoiding%20sleeping%20on%20your%20stomach%20if%20you%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20tested%20the%20best%20memory%20foam%20mattresses%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20laser%20thermometer%20pointed%20at%20the%20surface%20of%20a%20mattress%20reading%2073%20degrees%20during%20testing.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6216a516081b260018409b0f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20use%20a%20laser%20thermometer%20to%20test%20heat%20dissipation%20for%20each%20mattress.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E