0felt%20any%20pain.%20I%20also%20used%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-41128-20%26h%3Df6856a57680732ca0b5a242a35ec38f03f86d88d59a3b7eaf8b2eabcd949945d%26postID%3D61b8efc6f2a36b1ac9f419a8%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbest-foam-mattress%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.garmin.com%252Fen-US%252Fp%252F621922%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGarmin%20Forerunner%20945%20watch%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20track%20how%20much%20REM%2C%20deep%2C%20and%20overall%20sleep%20I%20had.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMotion%20transfer%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAlso%20called%20motion%20isolation%2C%20motion%20transfer%20is%20measured%20using%20the%20bowling%20ball%20test.%20I%20drop%20a%2015-pound%20bowling%20ball%20from%204%20feet%20above%20the%20mattress%20so%20that%20it%20lands%2012%20inches%20from%20a%20soda%20can.%20If%20the%20can%20falls%20over%2C%20the%20motion%20isolation%20is%20poor.%20If%20it%20stays%20upright%2C%20the%20bed%20does%20a%20good%20job%20of%20dampening%20motion.%20I%20also%20take%20a%20vibration%20meter%20reading%20from%20the%20opposite%20side%20of%20the%20bed%20from%20the%20bowling%20ball%20drop.%20Lastly%2C%20I%20note%20my%20subjective%20experience%20as%20others%20move%20around%20on%20the%20mattress%20while%20I'm%20lying%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgiphy.com%2Fembed%2F1HCMxCnViRs2TiB20r%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22360%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgiphy.com%2Fgifs%2Finsider-reviews-buying-guides-best-mattress-in-2021-1HCMxCnViRs2TiB20r%5C%22%3Evia%20GIPHY%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrial%20and%20warranty%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAll%20of%20the%20top%20mattresses%20in%20this%20guide%20have%20a%20trial%20period%20of%20at%20least%2090%20nights.%20That%20should%20be%20long%20enough%20to%20tell%20if%20a%20bed%20is%20right%20for%20you.%20I%20read%20the%20fine%20print%20of%20the%20return%20policy%20to%20see%20if%20any%20fees%20are%20associated%20with%20returning%20the%20bed.%20I%20also%20note%20the%20length%20of%20the%20warranty.%20Our%20picks%20have%20warranties%20of%20at%20least%2010%20years%2C%20about%20how%20long%20you%20should%20expect%20your%20mattress%20to%20last.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeat%20dissipation%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20first%20thing%20I%20do%20each%20morning%20is%20use%20a%20laser%20thermometer%20to%20measure%20the%20surface%20temperature%20of%20the%20mattress.%20The%20second%20thing%20I%20do%20is%20measure%20the%20surface%20temp%20again%20two%20minutes%20later.%20The%20first%20measurement%20tells%20me%20how%20cool%20the%20mattress%20stays.%20When%20I%20compare%20it%20to%20the%20second%20measurement%2C%20I%20see%20how%20well%20the%20heat%20dissipates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEdge%20support%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGood%20edge%20support%20is%20helpful%20whether%20you%20are%20lying%20or%20sitting%20on%20the%20side%20of%20your%20bed.%20You%20want%20to%20feel%20supported.%20To%20test%20edge%20support%2C%20I%20lie%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20bed%20and%20slowly%20roll%20off.%20I%20note%20the%20approximate%20angle%20of%20my%20body%20at%20the%20moment%20I%20fall.%20The%20closer%20I%20get%20to%20the%20perpendicular%2C%20the%20better%20the%20edge%20support.%20I%20also%20sit%20on%20the%20side%20of%20the%20bed%20and%20measure%20how%20much%20the%20edge%20sinks.%20On%20average%2C%20mattresses%20sink%20about%203.5%20inches.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESetup%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20set%20up%20all%20the%20mattresses%20myself%20(unless%20there's%20free%20white-glove%20delivery).%20I%20note%20how%20long%20it%20takes%20me%2C%20any%20unusual%20steps%2C%20if%20there's%20an%20initial%20odor%20and%20if%20it%20dissipates%20by%20bedtime%2C%20and%20if%20the%20mattress%20comes%20with%20directions%20or%20tools.%20Most%20mattresses%20take%205%20to%2010%20minutes%20to%20set%20up%20but%20do%20require%20a%20period%20to%20expand%20before%20being%20suitable%20for%20sleeping.%20I%20strongly%20recommend%20getting%20help%20setting%20up%20your%20mattress.%20I%20give%20the%20costs%20and%20details%20for%20white-glove%20delivery%20in%20my%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPortability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20have%20to%20move%20the%20mattresses%20around%20more%20than%20the%20average%20person%20as%20I%20switch%20them%20out%20in%20my%20testing%20area.%20Portability%20is%20important%20if%20you%20move%20a%20lot%20or%20just%20want%20to%20regularly%20rotate%20your%20bed%2C%20an%20important%20step%20to%20prolong%20the%20life%20of%20your%20mattress.%20When%20moving%20the%20mattresses%2C%20I%20note%20how%20heavy%20they%20feel%2C%20if%20they%20flop%20around%2C%20and%20if%20there%20are%20handles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20best%20memory%20foam%20mattress%20FAQs%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20pressing%20down%20on%20a%20mattress%20to%20show%20how%20much%20it%20sinks.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6230ed03dc43bd001894895f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFoam%20mattresses%20are%20generally%20more%20affordable%20than%20other%20types%2C%20but%20they%20may%20not%20last%20as%20long.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20memory%20foam%20mattresses%20get%20hot%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarly%20memory%20foam%20would%20absorb%20heat%20and%20get%20warmer%20over%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hales.%20%26quot%3BBut%20as%20memory%20foam%20has%20developed%20over%20the%20years%2C%20heat%20has%20become%20less%20of%20an%20issue.%26quot%3B%20Hales%20noted%20that%20even%20the%20best%20all-foam%20mattresses%20will%20run%20hotter%20than%20hybrid%20mattresses%2C%20which%20are%20designed%20for%20airflow%20and%20breathability.%20I've%20found%20that%20hybrid%20mattresses%20are%20generally%20cooler%20than%20all-foam%20mattresses%2C%20but%20some%20outliers%20tend%20to%20stay%20cool%2C%20including%20our%20top%20pick%2C%20the%20Tempur-Cloud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20much%20does%20a%20memory%20foam%20mattress%20cost%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20picks%20range%20in%20price%20from%20%24400%20to%20%244%2C600.%20You%20should%20expect%20to%20spend%20at%20least%20%241%2C000%20for%20a%20high-quality%2C%20all-foam%20mattress%20but%20can%20get%20away%20with%20spending%20less%20if%20you%20don't%20mind%20a%20bed%20that%20sleeps%20hot%20or%20has%20poor%20pressure%20relief%20or%20support.%20Foam%20beds%20tend%20to%20cost%20less%20than%20other%20mattress%20styles%2C%20but%20they%20lack%20the%20durability%20and%20support%20provided%20by%20the%20coils%20found%20in%20hybrid%20mattresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20memory%20foam%20mattresses%20more%20likely%20to%20cause%20allergic%20reactions%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Li%2C%20dust%20mites%20are%20the%20main%20source%20of%20allergic%20reactions%20to%20bedding.%20She%20pointed%20to%20a%20study%20that%20found%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fbooks%2FNBK560718%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E5%25%20to%2030%25%20of%20the%20general%20population%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20reactive%20to%20dust%20mites.%20Li%20suggested%20covering%20your%20mattress%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-mattress-protector%5C%22%3Ebest%20mattress%20protector%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20ward%20off%20dust%20mites.%C2%A0%20Formaldehyde%20is%20another%20source%20of%20allergic%20reactions%20to%20bedding%20that%20Li%20sees.%20Formaldehyde%20is%20used%20as%20a%20preservative%20in%20some%20mattresses.%20Look%20for%20beds%20with%20CertiPUR-US%20and%20Greenguard%20Gold%20certifications%20if%20you%20are%20sensitive%20to%20formaldehyde.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20I%20need%20to%20use%20a%20box%20spring%20or%20foundation%20with%20a%20memory%20foam%20mattress%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ENo.%20Memory%20foam%20mattresses%20require%20a%20solid%20or%20slatted%20foundation.%20If%20you%20choose%20a%20slatted%20foundation%2C%20ensure%20the%20slats%20are%20no%20more%20than%202.5%20inches%20apart.%20If%20they%20are%2C%20add%20a%20bunkie%20board%20or%20extra%20slats.%20Placing%20your%20mattress%20directly%20on%20the%20floor%20is%20also%20an%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-foam-mattress%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705093987000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f68be67323fc4001e0d7704%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-foam-mattress%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We've%20tested%2020%20memory%20foam%20mattresses%20to%20find%20the%20best%20to%20suit%20all%20sleep%20positions.%20Our%20top%20picks%20span%20cooling%2C%20firm%2C%20and%20affordable%20options.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jbrains%40businessinsider.com%20(James%20Brains)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-foam-mattress%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jonathan%20Majors%20Dropped%20From%20Dennis%20Rodman%20Movie%20After%20Assault%20Conviction%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705093966000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmajors-rodman-split.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D562%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235870489%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jonathan%20Majors%20has%20lost%20a%20buzzy%20upcoming%20film%20role%20after%20his%20recent%20assault%20conviction.%20The%20actor%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20playing%20controversial%20basketball%20pla