20consult%20a%20vet%20before%20you%20change%20their%20diet%20or%20feed%20them%20smaller%20portions.%20As%20your%20cat%20nears%20their%20first%20birthday%2C%20your%20vet%20can%20evaluate%20their%20weight%20and%20how%20many%20calories%20they%20should%20consume%20daily.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGuaranteed%20analysis%20and%20nutrient%20profiles%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20guaranteed%20analysis%20on%20a%20pet%20food%20label%20shows%20the%20percentages%20of%20important%20nutrients%2C%20including%20protein%2C%20fat%2C%20fiber%2C%20and%20other%20essential%20vitamins%20and%20minerals.%20Food%20for%20adult%20cats%2C%20including%20seniors%2C%20must%20have%20a%20minimum%20of%2026%25%20protein%20and%209%25%20fat.%20Our%20experts%20say%20it's%20important%20to%20carefully%20examine%20the%20guaranteed%20analysis%20of%20protein%2C%20fat%2C%20and%20fiber%20percentages%20to%20ensure%20the%20recipe%20meets%20your%20cat's%20needs.%20The%20best%20cat%20foods%20for%20weight%20loss%20generally%20contain%20low%20to%20moderate%20fat%20and%20high%20fiber.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIngredients%20list%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20ingredients%20on%20a%20pet%20food%20label%20appear%20in%20order%20of%20weight.%20As%20obligate%20carnivores%2C%20cats%20must%20eat%20diets%20made%20up%20of%20animal-based%20proteins.%20So%2C%20animal%20proteins%20in%20the%20form%20of%20whole%20meat%2C%20meat%20meal%2C%20or%20animal%20byproducts%20should%20appear%20first%20on%20the%20ingredients%20list%20of%20any%20cat%20food.%20To%20add%20fiber%20to%20your%20cat's%20diet%20and%20keep%20them%20feeling%20full%20between%20meals%2C%20opt%20for%20recipes%20with%20whole%20complex%20carbohydrates%20such%20as%20whole%20corn%2C%20whole%20brown%20rice%2C%20oats%2C%20and%20inulin.%20Sources%20of%20inulin%20you%20may%20notice%20on%20cat%20food%20labels%20include%20chicory%20root%20and%2C%20less%20commonly%2C%20Jerusalem%20artichoke.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExpert%20formulations%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EExpert%20formulation%20is%20even%20more%20important%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20weight%20loss%20diets%20since%20the%20best%20cat%20foods%20for%20weight%20loss%20are%20developed%20to%20provide%20more%20nutrients%20per%20serving%2C%20with%20fewer%20calories.%20We%20only%20recommend%20food%20from%20brands%20that%20employ%20a%20full-time%20board-certified%20veterinary%20nutritionist%20or%20a%20PhD-level%20animal%20nutritionist.%20This%20helps%20ensure%20your%20cat's%20food%20meets%20nutritional%20recommendations%20and%20includes%20the%20right%20ingredients%20for%20cats.%20It%20also%20aligns%20with%20the%20WSAVA%20guidelines%20and%20our%20experts'%20guidance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManufacturing%20standards%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20expect%20commercial%20cat%20food%20brands%20to%20be%20transparent%20about%20their%20quality%20control%20measures.%20This%20means%20providing%20information%20about%20the%20types%20of%20tests%20they%20conduct%2C%20how%20often%20they%20test%2C%20and%20the%20results%20of%20those%20tests.%20If%20this%20information%20doesn't%20appear%20on%20a%20pet%20food%20company's%20website%2C%20brand%20representatives%20should%20provide%20the%20information%20upon%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECalorie%20content%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20calorie%20content%20of%20cat%20food%20is%20listed%20in%20kilocalories%20(kcals).%20Weight%20management%20foods%20generally%20have%20fewer%20calories%20per%20serving%20but%20are%20nutrient-dense%20to%20meet%20nutritional%20needs.%20However%2C%20the%20calorie%20needs%20of%20adult%20cats%20can%20vary%20depending%20on%20their%20age%2C%20ideal%20weight%2C%20and%20overall%20health.%20Our%20experts%20emphasize%20the%20importance%20of%20switching%20to%20a%20weight%20management%20diet%20instead%20of%20just%20giving%20your%20cat%20less%20food.%20Your%20vet%20can%20recommend%20the%20best%20cat%20foods%20for%20weight%20loss%20and%20the%20right%20portion%20size%20for%20your%20cat.%20When%20a%20pet%20is%20only%20a%20little%20overweight%20%E2%80%94%2010%25%20to%2015%25%20%E2%80%94%20a%20successful%20approach%20to%20weight%20loss%20may%20involve%20switching%20to%20a%20lower-calorie%20food%20and%20adjusting%20treats%20and%20snacks%2C%20combined%20with%20increased%20exercise%2C%20Churchill%20says.%20Pets%20more%20than%2015%25%20heavier%20than%20their%20ideal%20weight%20are%20considered%20obese%20and%20may%20benefit%20from%20a%20prescription%20weight%20loss%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVets%20can%20use%20a%20scale%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aaha.org%2Fglobalassets%2F02-guidelines%2Fweight-management%2Fweightmgmt_bodyconditionscoring.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebody%20condition%20scoring%20(BCS)%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20assess%20your%20cat's%20weight%20and%20body%20fat.%20Your%20vet%20will%20consider%20your%20cat's%20lifestyle%2C%20ideal%20weight%2C%20and%20overall%20health%20to%20recommend%20the%20ideal%20number%20of%20daily%20calories%20your%20cat%20should%20eat.%20You%20can%20ask%20your%20vet%20to%20teach%20you%20how%20to%20use%20the%20BCS%20system%20to%20check%20your%20cat's%20body%20fat%20at%20home%20between%20wellness%20visits.%20Churchill%20says%20that%20frequent%20monitoring%20of%20your%20cat's%20weight%20is%20important%20since%20it%20allows%20veterinarians%20to%20fine-tune%20caloric%20intake%20and%20ensure%20that%20weight%20loss%20stays%20safe%20and%20healthy.%20She%20adds%20that%20cats%20should%20lose%20weight%20gradually%2C%20at%20a%20rate%20of%201%25%20to%202%25%20of%20their%20body%20weight%20per%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20selected%20the%20best%20cat%20foods%20for%20weight%20loss%3Cp%3ETo%20select%20the%20best%20cat%20foods%20for%20weight%20loss%2C%20we%20consulted%20four%20veterinarians%2C%20including%20three%20specializing%20in%20animal%20nutrition.%20Our%20experts%20didn't%20recommend%20specific%20foods%2C%20but%20they%20helped%20us%20determine%20what%20makes%20an%20effective%20weight%20loss%20food%20and%20how%20to%20ensure%20your%20cat%20loses%20weight%20in%20a%20safe%20and%20healthy%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Deb%20Zoran%20is%20a%20board-certified%20small%20animal%20internist%2C%20nutritionist%2C%20and%20professor%20of%20small%20animal%20clinical%20sciences%20at%20the%20School%20of%20Veterinary%20Medicine%20and%20Biomedical%20Sciences%2C%20Texas%20A%26amp%3BM%20University.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Korinn%20Saker%20is%20a%20board-certified%20veterinarian%2C%20a%20distinguished%20member%20of%20the%20American%20College%20of%20Veterinary%20Nutrition%2C%20and%20a%20professor%20of%20clinical%20nutrition%20at%20the%20College%20of%20Veterinary%20Medicine%2C%20North%20Carolina%20State%20University.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Julie%20Churchill%20is%20a%20board-certified%20veterinary%20nutritionist%20and%20a%20professor%20of%20nutrition%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Minnesota%20College%20of%20Veterinary%20Medicine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Mark%20Freeman%20is%20a%20board-certified%20veterinarian%20and%20assistant%20professor%20of%20community%20practice%20at%20Virginia-Maryland%20College%20of%20Veterinary%20Medicine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20consulted%20guidelines%20and%20recommendations%20from%20the%20AAFCO%2C%20the%20WSAVA%20Global%20Nutrition%20Guidelines%2C%20and%20other%20publications%20and%20organizations%20linked%20in%20this%20guide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWeight%20loss%20cat%20food%20FAQs%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20best%20food%20to%20feed%20my%20overweight%20cat%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20cat%20foods%20for%20weight%20loss%20are%20formulated%20for%20and%20labeled%20as%20%26quot%3Bweight%20management%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bweight%20loss%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bhealthy%20weight%26quot%3B%20cat%20food.%20Weight%20management%20cat%20foods%20typically%20have%20less%20calories%20and%20fat%20and%20more%20nutrients%20per%20serving%20than%20regular%20cat%20food.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20no%20single%20best%20food%20for%20all%20overweight%20cats.%20The%20ideal%20food%20for%20your%20cat%20will%20depend%20on%20their%20individual%20needs%2C%20age%2C%20ideal%20weight%2C%20and%20overall%20health.%20That's%20why%20it's%20important%20to%20consult%20your%20vet%20before%20making%20changes%20to%20your%20cat's%20diet.%20They%20can%20help%20you%20choose%20the%20right%20food%20and%20develop%20a%20safe%20and%20effective%20weight%20loss%20plan%20for%20your%20cat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20do%20I%20get%20my%20indoor%20cat%20to%20lose%20weight%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EA%20weight%20management%20diet%20plays%20an%20important%20role%20in%20weight%20loss%2C%20but%20food%20is%20just%20one%20of%20the%20pillars%20of%20an%20effective%20weight%20loss%20plan%20for%20cats.%20Freeman%20stresses%20the%20importance%20of%20portion%20control.%20He%20and%20his%20team%20provide%20pet%20parents%20with%20a%20carefully%20calibrated%20measuring%20cup%20for%20dispensing%20food.%20Churchill%20recommends%20using%20a%20kitchen%20scale%20to%20measure%20portions%20accurately.%20Keep%20in%20mind%20that%20treats%20also%20count%20toward%20your%20cat's%20daily%20calories.%20Because%20treats%20are%20typically%20empty%20calories%2C%20which%20means%20they're%20not%20complete%20and%20balanced%2C%20Churchill%20recommends%20giving%20your%20cat%20a%20small%20portion%20of%20their%20meal%20as%20a%20reward%20instead.%20Exercise%20is%20also%20essential%2C%20especially%20for%20indoor%20cats%2C%20since%20it%20burns%20calories%20and%20helps%20keep%20cats%20from%20getting%20bored.%20Churchill%20recommends%20offering%20food%20from%20a%20feeder%20puzzle%2C%20and%20all%20of%20our%20experts%20agree%20that%20cat%20trees%20and%20perches%20are%20important%20additions%20to%20your%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-cat-foods-weight-loss%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705090063000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https