%2C%20Kiran%20Patel%2C%20Bhargav%20Darji%2C%20Sandip%20Patel%2C%20Piyush%20Barot%2C%20Arpitsinh%20Zala%2C%20Biren%20Patel%2C%20Jayesh%20Patel%20and%20Sam%20Paaji%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20booked%20on%20the%20charge%20of%20human%20trafficking%20under%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%20section%20370%2C%20for%20destroying%20evidence%20(section%20201)%20and%20criminal%20conspiracy%20(section%20120-B).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20revealed%20that%20these%20agents%20had%20promised%20to%20help%20the%20passengers%20from%20Gujarat%20to%20enter%20the%20US%20illegally%20after%20reaching%20the%20Latin%20American%20country%20(Nicaragua)%20for%20Rs%2060%20lakh%20to%20Rs%2080%20lakh%2C%20Additional%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%2C%20CID%20(Crime%20and%20Railways)%2C%20SP%20Rajkumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20came%20to%20light%20that%20before%20this%20flight%2C%20which%20was%20grounded%20in%20France%2C%20these%20agents%20who%20work%20closely%20with%20main%20agents%20living%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Mexico%2C%20Nicaragua%2C%20Dubai%20and%20Delhi%2C%20had%20sent%20several%20people%20to%20Nicaragua%20in%20three%20different%20batches%20in%20December%20alone%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20the%20statements%20of%20passengers%20from%20Gujarat%2C%20we%20have%20identified%20and%20booked%2014%20agents%20for%20human%20trafficking.%20Since%20they%20had%20forced%20the%20passengers%20to%20delete%20audio%20files%20and%20other%20trip-related%20contents%20from%20their%20mobile%20phones%2C%20we%20have%20also%20added%20section%20201.%20Each%20passenger%20had%20agreed%20to%20pay%20Rs%2060%20lakh%20to%20Rs%2080%20lakh%20to%20these%20agents%20only%20after%20reaching%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rajkumar%20told%20reporters%20in%20Gandhinagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nicaragua-bound%20aircraft%20carrying%20260%20Indians%20was%20grounded%20in%20France%20for%20four%20days%20over%20suspected%20human%20trafficking%20last%20month.%20It%20landed%20in%20Mumbai%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20December%2026%20after%20it%20was%20sent%20back.%20These%20Indians%20included%2066%20from%20Gujarat%2C%20who%20were%20then%20questioned%20by%20the%20CID%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20investigation%20into%20the%20suspected%20human%20trafficking%20conspiracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agents%20had%20told%20the%20passengers%20that%20their%20men%20would%20take%20them%20to%20the%20US%20border%20in%20Mexico%20from%20Nicaragua%20and%20then%20help%20them%20cross%20the%20border.%20It%20also%20came%20to%20light%20that%20the%20agents%20had%20booked%20air%20tickets%20for%20these%20passengers%2C%20said%20Mr%20Rajkumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20plan%20devised%20by%20the%20agents%2C%20these%2066%20passengers%20reached%20Dubai%20on%20valid%20tourist%20visas%20from%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Mumbai%20and%20Delhi%20between%20December%2010%20and%2020.%20As%20directed%20by%20the%20agents%2C%20these%20passengers%20boarded%20the%20Nicaragua-bound%20aircraft%20of%20a%20private%20airline%20at%20the%20Fujairah%20International%20Airport%20on%20December%2021%2C%20the%20release%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chartered%20flight%2C%20which%20was%20operated%20by%20Romanian%20charter%20company%20Legend%20Airlines%20and%20bound%20for%20Nicaragua%2C%20landed%20at%20Vatry%20near%20Paris%20on%20December%2021%20for%20a%20technical%20stopover%20en%20route%20from%20Dubai%20when%20the%20French%20police%20intervened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigations%20so%20far%20revealed%20that%20all%20the%20flight%20bookings%20were%20done%20by%20Delhi-based%20agents%20and%20they%20also%20keep%20their%20lawyers%20ready%20if%20anything%20goes%20wrong%2C%20Mr%20Rajkumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20nearly%20200%20people%20from%20Punjab%20on%20that%20flight%2C%20while%2066%20were%20from%20Gujarat.%20We%20learnt%20that%20these%20trips%20are%20mainly%20for%20Punjabis.%20If%20some%20seats%20remain%20vacant%20on%20the%20flight%20after%20accommodating%20them%2C%20the%20Delhi%20agents%20ask%20Gujarat-based%20agents%20to%20arrange%20people%20who%20are%20ready%20to%20pay%20to%20enter%20the%20US%20illegally%20through%20their%20setup%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20agents%20instructed%20the%20passengers%20from%20Punjab%20to%20identify%20themselves%20as%20Khalistani%20and%20seek%20asylum%20in%20the%20US%20if%20the%20US%20police%20catch%20them%20at%20the%20border.%20The%20story%20will%20be%20different%20for%20other%20passengers.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20the%20government%20allows%20asylum%20seekers%20to%20work%20on%20humanitarian%20grounds%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20no%20arrest%20has%20been%20made%20so%20far%20and%20a%20look-out%20circular%20will%20soon%20be%20issued%20against%20all%2014%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705084980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fb5ee70sg_mumbai-passengers-france_625x300_27_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fif-caught-in-us-punjab-fliers-on-donkey-flight-were-told-to-say-4851781%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Weeks%20after%20a%20Nicaragua-bound%20plane%20carrying%20Indians%20was%20grounded%20in%20France%2C%20the%20Gujarat%20police%20has%20booked%2014%20agents%20on%20the%20charge%20of%20human%20trafficking%20for%20trying%20to%20send%20more%20than%2060%20persons%20from%20Gujarat%20to%20the%20US%20illegally.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fif-caught-in-us-punjab-fliers-on-donkey-flight-were-told-to-say-4851781%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fif-caught-in-us-punjab-fliers-on-donkey-flight-were-told-to-say-485