dard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fahead-of-ipo-medi-assist-mobilises-rs-351-crore-from-anchor-investors-124011300004_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fahead-of-ipo-medi-assist-mobilises-rs-351-crore-from-anchor-investors-124011300004_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNot%20Seeking%20To%20Destroy%20Palestinian%20People%26quot%3B%2C%20Says%20Israel%20In%20Genocide%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsrael%20said%20Friday%20it%20was%20not%20seeking%20to%20destroy%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%20as%20it%20hit%20back%20at%20what%20it%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bprofoundly%20distorted%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmalevolent%26quot%3B%20genocide%20case%20against%20it%20at%20the%20UN's%20top%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa%20has%20launched%20an%20emergency%20case%20at%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20(ICJ)%20arguing%20that%20Israel%20stands%20in%20breach%20of%20the%20UN%20Genocide%20Convention%2C%20signed%20in%201948%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Holocaust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPretoria%20wants%20judges%20to%20force%20Israel%20to%20%26quot%3Bimmediately%26quot%3B%20stop%20the%20Gaza%20campaign%20launched%20after%20the%20October%207%20Hamas%20attacks%20that%20killed%201%2C140%20people%2C%20according%20to%20an%20AFP%20tally%20based%20on%20Israeli%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2023%2C469%20people%2C%20mostly%20women%20and%20children%2C%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Israel's%20offensive%2C%20according%20to%20Gaza's%20Hamas-run%20health%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETal%20Becker%2C%20a%20top%20lawyer%20representing%20Israel%2C%20said%20South%20Africa%20had%20%26quot%3Bregrettably%20put%20before%20the%20court%20a%20profoundly%20distorted%20factual%20and%20legal%20picture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20videos%20and%20pictures%2C%20Becker%20painted%20a%20graphic%20image%20of%20the%20horrors%20of%20the%20October%207%20attacks%20for%20the%20robed%20judges%20in%20the%20Peace%20Palace%20in%20The%20Hague%2C%20where%20the%20ICJ%20sits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20%26quot%3Btortured%20children%20in%20front%20of%20parents%2C%20parents%20in%20front%20of%20children%20burned%20people...%20systematically%20raped%20and%20mutilated%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20stressed%20that%20Israel's%20response%20was%20in%20self-defense%20and%20not%20aimed%20at%20the%20Palestinian%20residents%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIsrael%20is%20in%20a%20war%20of%20defence%20against%20Hamas%2C%20not%20against%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Becker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20these%20circumstances%2C%20there%20can%20hardly%20be%20a%20charge%20more%20false%20and%20more%20malevolent%20than%20the%20allegation%20against%20Israel%20of%20genocide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Israel%20and%20its%20ally%20the%20United%20States%20have%20dismissed%20the%20case%20as%20groundless%20and%20vowed%20a%20robust%20defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20State%20of%20Israel%20is%20accused%20of%20genocide%20at%20a%20time%20when%20it%20is%20fighting%20genocide%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20hearings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20terrorist%20organisation%20carried%20out%20the%20worst%20crime%20against%20the%20Jewish%20people%20since%20the%20Holocaust%2C%20and%20now%20someone%20comes%20to%20defend%20it%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20Holocaust%3F%20What%20brazen%20gall.%20The%20world%20is%20upside%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Washington%2C%20State%20Department%20spokesman%20Matthew%20Miller%20said%20the%20South%20African%20case%20was%20%26quot%3Bunfounded%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICJ%20will%20likely%20rule%20within%20a%20matter%20of%20weeks%20on%20South%20Africa's%20request.%20Its%20rulings%20are%20final%20and%20legally%20binding%20but%20it%20has%20little%20power%20to%20enforce%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20month%20after%20Russia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20ICJ%20ordered%20a%20halt%20to%20the%20military%20operation%20--%20to%20no%20avail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Crossed%20the%20line'%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20emergency%20proceeding%2C%20the%20court%20will%20not%20rule%20on%20the%20fundamentals%20of%20the%20case%20--%20whether%20Israel%20is%20actually%20committing%20genocide%20--%20but%20on%20whether%20the%20rights%20of%20Gazans%20to%20exist%20are%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa%20can%20bring%20an%20ICJ%20case%20against%20Israel%20as%20both%20countries%20have%20signed%20the%20Genocide%20Convention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPretoria's%20Justice%20Minister%20Ronald%20Lamola%20told%20the%20court%20on%20Thursday%20that%20Israel%20had%20%26quot%3Bcrossed%20the%20line%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20in%20breach%20of%20the%20convention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20even%20the%20brutality%20of%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20could%20not%20justify%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGenocides%20are%20never%20declared%20in%20advance%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Adila%20Hassim%2C%20a%20top%20lawyer%20for%20South%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20this%20court%20has%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20past%2013%20weeks%20of%20evidence%20that%20shows%20incontrovertibly%20a%20pattern%20of%20conduct%20and%20related%20intention%20that%20justifies%20a%20plausible%20claim%20of%20genocidal%20acts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20African%20National%20Congress%20(ANC)%20has%20long%20been%20a%20firm%20supporter%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20cause%2C%20often%20linking%20it%20to%20its%20own%20struggle%20against%20the%20white-minority%20apartheid%20government%2C%20which%20had%20cooperative%20relations%20with%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnti-apartheid%20icon%20Nelson%20Mandela%20famously%20said%20South%20Africa's%20freedom%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bincomplete%20without%20the%20freedom%20of%20the%20Palestinians%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20ICJ%20on%20Thursday%2C%20the%20lawyer%20for%20South%20Africa%20Blinne%20Ni%20Ghralaigh%20said%20international%20justice%20itself%20was%20on%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20might%20say%20that%20the%20very%20reputation%20of%20international%20law%2C%20its%20ability%20and%20will%20to%20bind%20and%20protect%20all%20peoples%20equally%2C%20hangs%20in%20the%20balance%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705084560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Ftlmr4nio_gaza_625x300_30_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-gaza-palestine-not-seeking-to-destroy-palestinian-people-says-israel-at-top-un-court-4849187%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israel%20said%20Friday%20it%20was%20not%20seeking%20to%20destroy%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%20as%20it%20hit%20back%20at%20what%20it%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bprofoundly%20distorted%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmalevolent%26quot%3B%20genocide%20case%20against%20it%20at%20the%20UN's%20top%20court.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-gaza-palestine-not-seeking-to-destroy-palestinian-people-says-israel-at-top-un-court-4849187%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-gaza-palestine-not-seeking-to-destroy-palestinian-people-says-israel-at-top-un-court-4849187%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-gaza-palestine-not-seeking-to-destroy-palestinian-people-says-israel-at-top-un-court-4849187%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Expensive%20things%20owned%20by%20