22%26quot%3BNose%20Cover%26quot%3B%3A%20All%20About%20The%20New%20Gen%20Z%20Trend%20Taking%20Over%20Internet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFrom%20millennial%20pout%20to%20the%20peace%20sign%2C%20there%20have%20been%20several%20poses%20that%20have%20hung%20around%20for%20decades.%20However%2C%20now%20the%20%26quot%3Bnose%20cover%26quot%3B%20pose%20has%20left%20a%20lot%20of%20adults%20scratching%20their%20heads%20over%20what%20it%20might%20mean.%20Gen%20Z%20children%20everywhere%20seem%20to%20be%20hopping%20on%20this%20trend%2C%20including%20Tyson%20Fury's%2014-year-old%20daughter%20Venezuela%2C%20who%20has%20been%20seen%20covering%20her%20face%20in%20a%20family%20picture%20posted%20on%20mum%20Paris%20Fury's%20Instagram%20along%20with%20Paris'%20niece%20Valentino.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20Instagram%20story%20Boxer%20Tyson%20Fury's%20wife%2C%20Paris%20shared%20a%20photo%20as%20she%20celebrated%20her%20niece's%2013th%20birthday.%20Ms%20Paris%20posted%20a%20family%20photo%20to%20mark%20the%20occasion%20but%20her%20niece%20Valentino%2C%20and%20her%20eldest%20daughter%20Venezuela%20hid%20their%20faces%20behind%20their%20hands%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Bnose%20cover%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F01%2F11%2Flifestyle%2Fwhat-is-nose-cover-and-why-are-gen-z-teens-doing-it-in-family-photos%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20parents%20have%20been%20left%20baffled%20by%20this%20latest%20trend%20with%20many%20asking%20if%20it's%20a%20secret%20sign%20or%20a%20%26quot%3Btraveller%20thing%26quot%3B.%20One%20parent%2C%20Michelle%20Harris%2C%20infuriated%20by%20the%20family%20photos%20at%20Christmas%20being%20ruined%20by%20her%20teenage%20son%20using%20the%20'nose%20pose'%20even%20decided%20to%20confront%20him.%20%26quot%3BIs%20everything%20OK%3F%20Why%20won't%20you%20show%20up%20in%20family%20photos%20for%20the%20handsome%20boy%20that%20you%20are%20anymore%3F'%20Are%20you%20being%20bullied%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20asked%20her%20son%2C%20as%20per%20the%20outlet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20her%20son's%20response%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bsurprise%26quot%3B%2C%20Ms%20Harris%20recalled.%20%26quot%3B'No%2C%20but%20I%20will%20be%20if%20you%20post%20pictures%20of%20me%20online%20without%20my%20consent!'%26quot%3B%20her%20son%20told%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outlet%20explained%20that%20teenagers%20nowadays%20are%20active%20online%20and%20often%20seek%20out%20embarrassing%20photos%20of%20each%20other%20on%20social%20media%20to%20%26quot%3Broast%26quot%3B%20them.%20Covering%20their%20faces%2C%20then%2C%20is%20a%20way%20to%20potentially%20evade%20teasing%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EPost%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20parents%2C%20we%20want%20to%20capture%20it%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Harris%20said.%20%26quot%3BTheir%20first%20step%2C%20every%20tooth%2C%20the%20braces%2C%20the%20spots%20and%20then%20we%20proudly%20post%20in%20our%20online%20social%20circles%20mindlessly%20without%20stopping%20to%20think%20how%20damaging%20this%20can%20be%20to%20our%20youngsters%20within%20their%20own%20online%20social%20groups%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpics-once-asias-most-eligible-bachelor-brunei-prince-marries-a-commoner-4848453%5C%22%3EPics%3A%20Once%20Asia's%20Most%20Eligible%20Bachelor%2C%20Brunei%20Prince%20Marries%20A%20Commoner%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20speaking%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Ffabulous%2F25295727%2Fparis-fury-daughter-nose-cover-meaning%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Sun%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20parenting%20expert%20Amanda%20Jenner%20also%20attributed%20the%20budding%20trend%20to%20teenagers'%20acne-riddled%20awkward%20phase.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20to%20remember%20that%20this%20phase%20is%20a%20normal