talk%20about%20every%20state%2C%20but%20when%20we%20talk%20about%20a%20place%20where%20two%20or%20four%20of%20us%20(parties)%20have%20a%20strong%20presence%2C%20we%20think%20about%20it%20from%20the%20perspective%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20Punjab%2C%20where%20some%20leaders%20from%20both%20parties%20have%20opposed%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20other%2C%20Mr%20Khurshid%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhatever%20we%20do%2C%20we%20will%20do%20it%20together.%20We%20are%20holding%20discussions%20keeping%20the%20people%20and%20our%20party%20workers%20in%20mind.%20We%20will%20take%20a%20decision%20on%20whatever%20seats%20we%20can%20and%20place%20it%20before%20our%20leaders%2C%20and%20then%20decide%20on%20the%20next%20batch%20of%20seats.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilar%20sentiments%20were%20expressed%20by%20both%20parties%20after%20the%20first%20seat-sharing%20meeting%20on%20Monday.%20The%20Congress%20had%20said%20that%20it%20had%20decided%20to%20contest%20elections%20together%20with%20the%20AAP.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20senior%20AAP%20leader%20from%20Delhi%2C%20Gopal%20Rai%2C%20said%20that%20his%20party%20had%20stated%20its%20stand%20to%20contest%20the%20polls%20in%20five%20states%20-%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Goa%2C%20and%20Delhi%20-%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20according%20to%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunjab%20has%2013%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20and%20Delhi%20has%20seven.%20The%20BJP%20had%20swept%20all%20seven%20seats%20in%20Delhi%20in%202019%20while%20the%20Congress%20had%20won%20eight%20in%20Punjab.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705080660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F7lt3unvo_raghav-chadha-rajya-sabha_625x300_04_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fball-by-ball-commentary-raghav-chadha-on-congress-alliance-talks-4851420%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%2