om%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Favalon-technologies-joins-meity-s-rudra-supercomputing-mission-124011201027_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20partnership%20will%20add%20to%20the%20indigenous%20manufacturing%20capability%20of%20High-Performance%20Computing%20(HPC)%20systems%20that%20are%20a%20part%20of%20the%20'RUDRA'%20programme%2C%20said%20the%20company%20in%20an%20announcement%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Favalon-technologies-joins-meity-s-rudra-supercomputing-mission-124011201027_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Favalon-technologies-joins-meity-s-rudra-supercomputing-mission-124011201027_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Favalon-technologies-joins-meity-s-rudra-supercomputing-mission-124011201027_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Dead%20Man'%20Comes%20Alive%20After%20Ambulance%20Hits%20Pothole%20In%20Haryana%3A%20Family%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20much-derided%20potholes%20-%20which%20have%20caused%20everything%20from%20annoyance%20and%20exasperation%20to%20injuries%20and%20even%20deaths%20-%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20literal%20lifesaver%20for%20an%2080-year-old%20man%20from%20Haryana%20on%20Thursday%2C%20his%20family%20has%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeclared%20dead%20by%20doctors%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bbody%26quot%3B%20of%20Darshan%20Singh%20Brar%20was%20being%20taken%20from%20Patiala%20to%20his%20home%20near%20Karnal%2C%20where%20mourning%20relatives%20had%20gathered%2C%20food%20had%20been%20laid%20out%20and%20wood%20had%20been%20collected%20for%20his%20funeral%2C%20when%20the%20ambulance%20hit%20a%20pothole.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrar's%20family%20said%20his%20grandson%2C%20who%20was%20with%20him%20in%20the%20ambulance%2C%20noticed%20him%20moving%20his%20hand%20and%2C%20on%20sensing%20a%20heartbeat%2C%20asked%20the%20ambulance%20driver%20to%20head%20to%20the%20nearest%20hospital.%20The%20doctors%20there%20declared%20him%20alive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2080-year-old%20heart%20patient%20is%20now%20undergoing%20treatment%20at%20a%20hospital%20in%20Karnal%2C%20where%20his%20condition%20is%20said%20to%20be%20critical.%20The%20family%20has%20hailed%20the%20incident%20as%20a%20miracle%20and%20are%20now%20hoping%20for%20a%20speedy%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDespair%20To%20Hope%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Brar's%20grandsons%2C%20Balwan%20Singh%2C%20said%20the%2080-year-old%20lived%20in%20Nising%20near%20Karnal%2C%20where%20an%20entire%20colony%20has%20been%20named%20after%20him.%20Brar%20had%20not%20been%20keeping%20well%20for%20a%20few%20days%20and%20Balwan%20Singh's%20brother%20took%20him%20to%20a%20hospital%20near%20his%20house%20in%20Patiala%20for%20treatment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalwan%20said%20his%20grandfather%20was%20on%20a%20ventilator%20for%20four%20days%20and%2C%20on%20Thursday%20morning%2C%20doctors%20said%20that%20his%20heartbeat%20had%20stopped.%20He%20was%20taken%20off%20the%20ventilator%20and%20declared%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20brother%20in%20Patiala%20informed%20us%20around%209%20am%20on%20Thursday%20about%20our%20grandfather's%20death%2C%20and%20he%20was%20getting%20him%20to%20Nising%20(roughly%20100%20km%20away)%20in%20an%20ambulance%20for%20his%20last%20rites.%20We%20had%20informed%20our%20relatives%20and%20other%20local%20residents%20who%20knew%20him%20and%20they%20had%20already%20gathered%20to%20mourn%20his%20passing.%20A%20tent%20had%20been%20set%20up%20and%20food%20had%20also%20been%20arranged%20for%20the%20mourners.%20We%20had%20also%20got%20wood%20for%20the%20cremation%2C%26quot%3B%20Balwan%20said%20on%20Friday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20ambulance%20was%20near%20Dhand%20village%20in%20Haryana's%20Kaithal%2C%20it%20hit%20a%20pothole%20hard%20and%20Balwan's%20brother%20noticed%20that%20Brar%20had%20moved%20his%20hand.%20Amazed%2C%20he%20checked%20for%20a%20heartbeat%20and%2C%20on%20sensing%20one%2C%20took%20the%2080-year-old%20to%20a%20hospital%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20said%20doctors%20at%20the%20hospital%20confirmed%20that%20Brar%20was%20alive%20and%20breathing%20and%20then%20referred%20him%20to%20a%20hospital%20in%20Nising%2C%20from%20where%20he%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20NP%20Rawal%20Hospital%20in%20Karnal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20miracle.%20Now%20we%20are%20hoping%20that%20my%20grandfather%20recovers%20soon.%20Everyone%20who%20had%20gathered%20to%20mourn%20his%20death%20congratulated%20us%2C%20and%20we%20requested%20them%20to%20have%20the%20food%20we%20had%20arranged.%20It%20is%20God's%20grace%20that%20he%20is%20now%20breathing%20and%20we%20are%20hoping%20he%20will%20get%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Critical%2C%20But%20Breathing'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Netrapal%20from%20Rawal%20Hospital%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20cannot%20say%20that%20the%20patient%20had%20died.%20When%20he%20was%20brought%20to%20us%2C%20he%20was%20breathing%20and%20had%20blood%20pressure%20as%20well%20as%20a%20pulse.%20We%20don't%20know%20what%20happened%20at%20the%20other%20hospital%2C%20whether%20it%20was%20a%20technical%20error%20or%20something%20else.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20family%20said%20he%20was%20on%20a%20ventilator%20in%20Patiala%20for%20four%20days%20but%20he%20is%20now%20breathing%20on%20his%20own.%20He%20is%20still%20critical%20and%20in%20the%20ICU.%20The%20breathing%20is%20laborious%20because%20he%20has%20an%20infection%20in%20his%20chest%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20doctor%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705077000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Frd08lb48_dead-man-comes-alive-haryana_625x300_12_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2