%20of%20the%20Second%20Series%20of%20the%20Selected%20Works%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20available%20online%20at%20nehruselectedworks.com%2C%26quot%3B%20Congress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BContrary%20to%20what%20Trivedi%20claims%2C%20these%20constitute%20no%20great%20revelation.%20Nehru%20was%20completely%20transparent%20and%20left%20behind%20written%20records%20-%20written%20by%20him%20personally.%20Here%20is%20some%20correspondence%20on%20the%20subject%20that%20Mr%20Trivedi%20did%20not%20exhibit%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ramesh%20said%2C%20attaching%20a%20few%20pages%20of%20the%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESudanshu%20Trivedi%20has%20apparently%20waved%20some%20letters%20on%20air%20-%20of%20Pandit%20Nehru%20on%20the%20Somnath%20Temple.%20These%20and%20many%20other%20letters%20of%20Nehru%2C%20including%20to%20then%20Home%20Minister%20Rajaji%20and%20President%20Rajendra%20Prasad%2C%20are%20all%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20and%20form%20part%20of%20Vol%2016-I%20of%20the%20Second...%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FjiL6wRzJCZ%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FjiL6wRzJCZ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20(%40Jairam_Ramesh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1745453654981947484%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2011%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trivedi%20had%20alleged%20Nehru%20opposed%20the%20association%20of%20Prasad%20and%20some%20Congress%20leaders%20with%20the%20rebuilding%20and%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Somnath%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comment%20came%20after%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20party%20colleagues%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20%26quot%3Brespectfully%20declined%26quot%3B%20the%20invitation%20to%20attend%20the%20Ram%20temple's%20consecration%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Ayodhya.%20The%20Congress%20has%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20making%20the%20consecration%20a%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20project%26quot%3B%20for%20electoral%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20other%20top%20BJP%20leaders%20will%20attend%20the%20Ram%20temple's%20consecration%20on%20January%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Nehru's%20letter%20of%20March%2011%2C%201951%2C%20shared%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20told%20the%20then%20Home%20Minister%20C%20Rajagopalachari%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20wrote%20to%20him%20that%20while%20there%20was%20obviously%20no%20objection%20to%20his%20visiting%20this%20temple%20or%20any%20other%20temple%20or%20other%20place%20of%20worship%20normally%2C%20on%20this%20particular%20occasion%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20temple%20would%20have%20a%20certain%20significance%20and%20certain%20implications.%20Therefore%2C%20for%20my%20part%2C%20I%20would%20have%20preferred%20if%20he%20did%20not%20associate%20himself%20in%20this%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20President%20is%20also%20anxious%20to%20associate%20himself%20with%20this%20function%2C%20I%20do%20not%20know%20whether%20it%20is%20desirable%20for%20me%20to%20insist%20that%20he%20should%20not%20do%20so.%20I%20propose%2C%20therefore%2C%20subject%20to%20your%20advice%2C%20to%20tell%20him%20that%20he%20can%20exercise%20his%20own%20discretion%20in%20the%20matter%2C%20although%2C%20I%20still%20think%20that%20it%20would%20be%20better%20for%20him%20not%20to%20go%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Nehru%20said%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2013%2C%201951%2C%20Nehru%20also%20wrote%20to%20Prasad%20on%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20Somnath%20temple%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20If%20you%20feel%20that%20it%20will%20not%20be%20right%20for%20you%20to%20refuse%20the%20invitation%2C%20I%20would%20not%20like%20to%20press%20my%20point%20any%20further%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C