ous%20lapse%20in%20(security)%20preparedness%20that%20cannot%20be%20overlooked%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20compromised%20security%20detail%20for%20a%20former%20chief%20minister%20not%20only%20jeopardises%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20individual%20but%20also%20raises%20questions%20about%20the%20broader%20commitment%20to%20ensuring%20the%20security%20and%20stability%20of%20the%20region%2C%E2%80%9D%20Beg%20said%2C%20while%20urging%20the%20administration%20to%20%E2%80%9Csafeguard%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20leaders%20who%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20the%20sociopolitical%20fabric%20of%20Kashmir.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20PDP%20has%20accused%20the%20administration%20of%20overlooking%20the%20security%20of%20Mehbooba%2C%20who%20was%20unceremoniously%20toppled%20as%20the%20last%20chief%20minister%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20state%20in%202018%2C%20when%20the%20BJP%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20coalition%20government%20with%20her%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20in%202019%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20had%20served%20a%20notice%20to%20Mehbooba%2C%20asking%20her%20to%20vacate%20the%20Fairview%20Residence%20on%20Srinagar%E2%80%99s%20upscale%20Gupkar%20Road%2C%20where%20she%20had%20been%20living%20since%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20receiving%20the%20notice%2C%20Mehbooba%2C%20who%20has%20served%20as%20a%20member%20of%20parliament%20representing%20Anantnag%20constituency%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20shifted%20to%20her%20sister%E2%80%99s%20residence%20in%20Khimber%20locality%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Srinagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20assessment%20by%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20and%20other%20security%20agencies%20has%20labelled%20the%20area%20as%20%E2%80%98unsafe%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%2C%20who%20has%20survived%20many%20assassination%20attempts%20in%20the%20past.%20Reportedly%2C%20it%20falls%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98track%E2%80%99%20used%20by%20militants%20to%20move%20into%20Srinagar%20from%20central%20and%20south%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20committee%20had%20recommended%20that%2010%20guard%20posts%2C%20five%20watch%20towers%2C%20one%20wireless%20grid%2C%20two%20access%20control%20units%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9Ctwo%20Detts%E2%80%9D%20be%20built%20for%20securing%20the%20Khimber%20house.%20However%2C%20a%20PDP%20leader%20said%20that%20no%20follow-up%20action%20was%20taken%20by%20the%20administration%20on%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20a%20security%20review%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20had%20warned%20that%20there%20are%20%E2%80%9Capprehensions%20of%20a%20terrorist%20attack%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%2C%20who%20resides%20with%20his%20mother%20and%20two%20daughters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAuthorities%20are%20urged%20to%20conduct%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20into%20the%20lapses%2C%20ensuring%20that%20any%20shortcomings%20are%20addressed%20promptly%20to%20prevent%20the%20recurrence%20of%20such%20incidents%20and%20to%20uphold%20the%20safety%20of%20political%20leaders%20in%20the%20region%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Beg.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705065509000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F04152043%2FScreenshot-2023-06-04-at-3.15.55-PM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fpdp-alleges-serious-security-lapses-responsible-for-mehbooba-muftis-road-accident-in-kashmir%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'The%20accident%20points%20towards%20the%20lack%20of%20detailed%20drill%20for%20a%20Z%2B%20protected%20person%20travelling%20on%20a%20highway%20which%20remains%20busy%20and%20has%20a%20history%20of%20targeted%20attacks%2C'%20said%20PDP%20general%20secretary%20Mehboob%20Beg.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fpdp-alleges-serious-securit