20lines%2C%20including%20the%20BJP%20and%20two%20former%20chief%20ministers%20(Jagannath%20Mishra%20and%20Lalu)%20figured%20in%20the%20fodder%20scam%20cases.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20cases%20pertained%20to%20the%20withdrawals%20from%20the%20treasuries%20worth%20Rs%20950%20crore%20in%20excess%20of%20budgetary%20allocations%20for%20the%20animal%20husbandry%20department%20over%20a%20span%20of%20sixteen%20years%20(1980-1996)%2C%20as%20pointed%20out%20in%20the%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%E2%80%99s%20reports%20then.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReacting%20to%20the%20ED%20naming%20Lalu%E2%80%99s%20daughters%20in%20its%20chargesheet%2C%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20spokesperson%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Manoj%20Jha%20said%20to%20the%20media%20in%20Delhi%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ED%20is%20doing%20this%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20two%20persons%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20power%20structure%20to%20trouble%20their%20political%20opponents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20fictitious%20case%20in%20which%20several%20FIRs%20were%20filed%20in%202008%2C%20and%20the%20CBI%20and%20the%20ED%20closed%20them%20in%202011%20after%20finding%20no%20evidence.%20The%20investigating%20agencies%20reopened%20it%20suddenly%20in%202021-22%2C%20when%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Operation%20Lotus%E2%80%99%20that%20worked%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20boomeranged%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20chargesheet%20in%20a%20special%20PMLA%20court%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20January%209%20is%20a%20clear-cut%20example%20of%20political%20vendetta.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJha%20cited%20how%20the%20leaders%20of%20Delhi%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Karnataka%20and%20Kerala%20%E2%80%93%20all%20non-BJP%20ruled%20states%20%E2%80%93%20were%20being%20targeted%20by%20the%20ED%20and%20the%20CBI.%20He%20apprehended%20that%20the%20investigating%20agencies%20may%20heap%20more%20trumped-up%20charges%20on%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20political%20rivals%20ahead%20of%20January%2022%2C%20the%20date%20of%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMedia%20focus%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20mainstream%20media%20%E2%80%93%20print%20and%20electronic%20%E2%80%93%20largely%20downplayed%20or%20ignored%20Jha%E2%80%99s%20statements.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20ED%20and%20CBI%20are%20issuing%20what%20Jha%20described%20as%20%E2%80%9Csummons%20after%20summons%E2%80%9D%20to%20opponents%20of%20the%20Hindutva%20party%20like%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20Hemant%20Soren%20and%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20cadres%20of%20the%20RSS%20and%20the%20BJP%20are%20moving%20door-to-door%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eakshat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20collect%20contributions%20from%20people%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Lord%20Ram%2C%20and%20Hindi%20newspapers%20from%20Patna%20to%20Lucknow%20and%20Delhi%20were%20full%20of%20stories%20on%20Ram%2C%20Sita%2C%20Ayodhya%2C%20Varanasi%20and%20Mathura.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIntentionally%20or%20otherwise%2C%20the%20visuals%20and%20narratives%20in%20the%20mass%20media%20are%20largely%20creating%20the%20perception%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20resurrected%20Lord%20Ram%20from%20the%20shackles%20of%20medieval%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eghulami%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(slavery)%20and%20restored%20him%20in%20the%20new%20temple%20being%20built%20on%20the%20site%20of%20the%20Babri%20Mosque%20in%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F_u29yrvIvg8%3Fsi%3DWdeLLR06UYMzVDmn%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20are%2C%20apparently%2C%20downplaying%20even%20the%20decisions%20of%20as%20many%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fsanatan-hindu-dharma-highest-guru-ram-temple%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efour%20Shankaracharyas%20to%20boycott%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20it%20disregards%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eshastras%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(scriptures)%2C%20and%20focusing%20mainly%20on%20the%20themes%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20and%20Ayodhya%20couched%20in%20news%20and%20advertisements%20for%20%E2%80%98Modi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esarkar%20ki%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eguarantee%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Lord%20Ram%20and%20Ayodhya%20have%20acquired%20all%20the%20newsworthiness%2C%20the%20myriad%20scams%20%E2%80%93%20Pegasus%2C%20the%20Rafale%20deals%2C%20the%20cloud%20over%20the%20PM-CARES%20fund%2C%20the%20disastrous%20consequences%20of%20demonetisation%2C%20and%20education%20and%20ration%20scams%20reported%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20%E2%80%93%20besides%20the%20unabating%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20and%20the%20selective%20bulldozing%20of%20minorities%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20appear%20to%20be%20topics%20of%20the%20distant%20past.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Will%20not%20be%20cowed%20down%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livehindustan.com%2Fbihar%2Fstory-why-are-lalu-yadav-nitish-kumar-hesitant-in-going-to-ayodhya-dham-sushil-modi-question-9169869.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESenior%20BJP%20leader%20Sushil%20Kumar%20Modi%20has%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20invited%20everyone%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Epran%20pratishtha%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%5Bconsecration%5D%20ceremony%20in%20Ayodhya%20and%20as%20such%2C%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20who%20offer%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echadar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emazar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Es%20and%20bow%20down%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Egurdwara%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Es%2C%20must%20attend%20the%20January%2022%20event.%20There%20should%20be%20no%20politics%20on%20such%20a%20divine%20occasion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20Hindutva%20cadres%20and%20supporters%20are%20heard%20discussing%20mirthfully%20how%20Nitish%2C%20Lalu%20as%20well%20as%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20%E2%80%93%20Samajwadi%20Party%20president%20and%20chief%20minister%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%93%20were%20in%20a%20%E2%80%98fix%E2%80%99%20over%20the%20issue%20and%20how%20they%20would%20likely%20suffer%20politically%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20RSS%20and%20BJP%20blowing%20up%20religious%20issues%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bihar%20media%20is%20largely%20agog%20with%20speculation%20about%20how%20Lalu%20was%20%E2%80%98pressuring%E2%80%99%20Nitish%20to%20make%20his%20son%20Tejashwi%20the%20CM%3B%20how%20Nitish%20is%20upset%20at%20not%20being%20nominated%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98convener%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%3B%20and%20how%20Nitish%20has%20been%20working%20on%20going%20back%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-alliance-parties-after-the-defeat-preparing-for-2024%5C%22%3EForging%20Genuine%20Solidarity%20With%20Each%20Other%20Is%20the%20Way%20Forward%20for%20the%20INDIA%20Alliance%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuch%20stories%20have%20been%20doing%20the%20rounds%20ever%20since%20the%20Bihar%20CM%20dumped%20the%20BJP%20in%20August%202022%20and%20joined%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20with%20the%20RJD%2C%20Congress%20and%20Left%20parties%2C%20despite%20leaders%20from%20his%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20and%20the%20RJD%20unequivocally%20denying%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20process%2C%20the%20news%20of%20over%204.5%20lakh%20youths%20getting%20jobs%3B%2065%25%20reservation%20for%20OBCs%2C%20SCs%2C%20STs%20and%20the%20extremely%20backward%20classes%3B%20as%20well%20as%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20work%20on%20education%2C%20health%20and%20infrastructure%20has%20been%20relegated%20to%20the%20periphery.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20that%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20(who%20are%20now%20also%20known%20as%20leaders%20of%20INDIA)%20are%20not%20unnerved%20by%20the%20developments.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COf%20course%2C%20we%20are%20anxious.%20The%20BJP%20under%20the%20cover%20of%20Ayodhya%20and%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20has%20let%20loose%20the%20investigating%20agencies%20to%20trouble%20Lalu%2C%20Tejashwi%20and%20others%20who%20are%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20saffron%20party%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jha%20said.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20will%20not%20be%20cowed%20down.%20We%20will%20take%20the%20battle%20to%20the%20court%20of%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fnalin-verma%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENalin%20Verma%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20author%2C%20media%20educator%2C%20and%20independent%20researcher%20in%20folklore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705064411000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29183927%2FThe-Wire-23.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Funnerved-by-ed-cbi-action-ahead-of-ayodhya-but-wont-be-cowed-down-rjds-manoj-jha%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20investigative%20agencies%20continue