uld%20be%20included%20in%20the%20existing%20%5BCAG%20Act%5D%20to%20make%20it%20mandatory%20for%20furnishing%20of%20information%20%5Bby%20the%20executive%5D%20in%20a%20time-bound%20manner%E2%80%9D%20(as%20paraphrased%20by%20%3Cem%3ETOI%3C%2Fem%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftransparency-in-modi-era-cags-working-shows-it-remains-opaque%5C%22%3ETransparency%20in%20Modi%20Era%3F%20CAG%E2%80%99s%20Working%20Shows%20It%20Remains%20Opaque%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20letter%20dated%20June%202014%20underlined%20that%20the%20proposed%20amendments%20had%20been%20under%20the%20finance%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20consideration%20for%20the%20preceding%20five%20years%20(i.e.%202009-2014).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20proposed%20draft%20amendment%20Bill%20to%20give%20the%20IAAD%20adequate%20powers%20was%20first%20submitted%20in%20November%202009.%20The%20CAG%E2%80%99s%20office%20had%20made%20subsequent%20revisions%20to%20the%20Bill%20based%20on%20suggestions%20by%20the%20finance%20ministry%2C%20and%20submitted%20a%20revised%20Bill%20in%20February%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20one%20looks%20at%20the%20debates%20of%20the%20constituent%20assembly%20of%20India%20while%20it%20framed%20the%20constitution%2C%20one%20will%20understand%20that%20the%20CAG%20and%20the%20IAAD%20were%20imagined%20as%20being%20independent%20of%20and%20autonomous%20from%20executive%20interference.%20So%2C%20such%20a%20dialogic%20and%20consultative%20approach%20should%20have%20evoked%20a%20positive%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadly%2C%20there%20had%20been%20complete%20silence%20from%20the%20ministry%20on%20this%20important%20matter.%20Jaitley%20and%20his%20party%20failed%20to%20give%20more%20powers%20to%20this%20constitutional%20institution%20during%20their%20first%20year%20in%20office%2C%20and%20the%20proposed%20amendments%20have%20not%20been%20in%20introduced%20in%20parliament%20till%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStrong%20audit%20findings%2C%20zero%20consequences%3A%20environment%20clearances%20and%20post-clearance%20monitoring%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2010%2C%202017%2C%20a%20performance%20audit%20on%20%E2%80%98Environmental%20Clearances%20and%20Post-Clearance%20Monitoring%20Mechanism%E2%80%99%20was%20tabled%20in%20parliament.%20While%20the%20audit%20findings%20and%20recommendations%20clearly%20pointed%20to%20the%20need%20to%20strengthen%20compliance%20with%20environmental%20regulations%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20actions%20have%20brazenly%20undermined%20this%20sane%20advice%20from%20the%20national%20auditor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrowing%20these%20findings%20away%2C%20the%20NDA%20government%20continued%20its%20race%20to%20the%20bottom%20in%20diluting%20environmental%20laws%20and%20facilitating%20the%20corporate%20takeover%20of%20natural%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adaniwatch.org%2Faudit_body_headed_by_modi_confidante_slams_approval_of_adani_port_expansion_at_dahej%5C%22%3Eperformance%20audit%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98Conservation%20of%20Coastal%20Ecosystems%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20tabled%20in%20parliament%20on%20August%208%2C%202022%20also%20pointed%20out%20brazen%20non-compliance%20with%20the%20EIA%20notification%20by%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20port%20expansion%20at%20Dahej.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F_BDqVanVhZo%3Fsi%3DZGrFC_-iQ4ivqy7Q%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERedacted%20audit%20reports%20on%20defence%20deals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAG%E2%80%99s%20audit%20report%20on%20Rafale%20has%20come%20under%20criticism%20for%20agreeing%20to%20editorial%20cuts%20from%20the%20audited%20entity%20on%20the%20matter%20of%20pricing.%20Usually%2C%20audit%20reports%20on%20defence%20matters%20only%20undergo%20such%20redaction%20as%20part%20of%20the%20protection%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20strategic%20interests.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Frafale-and-the-cag-a-case-of-redaction-ad-absurdum%5C%22%3EAnalysts%20believe%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20redactions%20in%20the%20Rafale%20report%20went%20much%20beyond%20such%20usual%20suggestions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAudit%20reports%20that%20were%20planned%20but%20never%20saw%20the%20light%20of%20the%20day%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20Josy%20Joseph%2C%20Shashi%20Kant%20Sharma%20had%20talked%20about%20undertaking%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fopinion%2Finterview%2Fwe-will-seek-audit-of-the-fiscal-impact-of-demonetisation%2Farticle17424354.ece%5C%22%3Ean%20audit%20of%20the%20fiscal%20impact%20of%20demonetisation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20his%20successor%20Rajiv%20Mehrishi%2C%20who%20took%20over%20on%20September%2025%2C%202017%2C%20did%20not%20pursue%20this%20thematic%20audit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDelayed%20audit%20reports%20and%20reduced%20output%20marked%20Rajiv%20Mehrishi%E2%80%99s%20years%20as%20CAG%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20before%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20impacted%20work%20at%20the%20national%20audit%20office%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Fcag-delayed-audit-reports-lower-output-defence-services%5C%22%3Ethere%20were%20signs%20that%20the%20machinery%20was%20slowing%20down%3C%2Fa%3E.%20During%20the%20year%202017-18%2C%20the%20CAG%20prepared%20only%2098%20audit%20reports%20in%20total%2C%20and%20in%202018-19%2C%20it%20prepared%20only%2073%20audit%20reports%20in%20total.%20In%202020%2C%20Mehrishi%20signed%20a%20bulk%20of%20audit%20reports%20in%20his%20last%20week%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20slowing%20down%20of%20the%20auditing%20processes%20since%202017%20was%20also%20accompanied%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F967903%2Ftabling-of-cag-reports-in-parliament-is-frequently-being-delayed-helping-government-evade-scrutiny%5C%22%3Eprolonged%20delays%20in%20the%20tabling%20of%20audit%20reports%20in%20parliament%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20ruling%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENon-transparent%20process%20of%20selecting%20the%20CAG%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20years%2C%20concerned%20citizens%20have%20been%20left%20wondering%20if%20the%20by%20process%20by%20which%20the%20CAG%20is%20selected%20is%20completely%20arbitrary%20and%20goes%20against%20the%20grain%20of%20what%20was%20envisaged%20during%20the%20debates%20of%20the%20constituent%20assembly%20of%20India%20while%20framing%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESelecting%20a%20senior%20administrative%20services%20officer%20who%20has%20worked%20in%20proximity%20to%20those%20in%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20does%20raise%20certain%20doubts%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20the%20public.%20Sometimes%20this%20arbitrary%20process%2C%20wherein%20the%20prime%20minister%20suggests%20to%20the%20president%20one%20name%20out%20of%20a%20shortlist%20prepared%20by%20the%20cabinet%2C%20creates%20an%20obvious%20conflict%20of%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcag-selection-auditor-prime-minister-government%5C%22%3EThe%20Process%20of%20Selecting%20the%20CAG%20Cannot%20Evade%20Accountability%20%E2%80%93%20Like%20it%20Has%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETweaking%20of%20follow-up%20performance%20audit%20plans%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsually%2C%20the%20senior%20management%20of%20the%20CAG%E2%80%99s%20office%20undertakes%20follow-up%20performance%20audits%20every%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20if%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fquestions-cag-auditors-failed-to-probe-in-its-mizoram-report%5C%22%3Efunctioning%20of%20the%20Building%20and%20Other%20Construction%20Workers%E2%80%99%20Welfare%20Boards%3C%2Fa%3E%20(BOCWWBs)%20across%20states%20and%20Union%20territories%20came%20under%20a%20comprehensive%20performance%20audit%20during%20the%20activity%20year%202008-09%20(reviewing%20their%20performance%20between%202003%20and%202008)%2C%20the%20next%20follow-up%20performance%20audit%20across%20states%20would%20take%20place%20during%20the%20activity%20year%202013-14%20(reviewing%20performance%20between%202008%20and%202013).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20follow-up%20performance%20audits%20have%20not%20been%20taken%20up%20across%20all%20states.%20This%20is%20strange%20and%20points%20to%20the%20lethargic%20attitude%20of%20the%20leadership.%20The%20pandemic%20year%20(2020-21)%20made%20it%20all%20the%20more%20crucial%20to%20know%20whether%20the%20BOCWWBs%20met%20their%20stated%20goals%20of%20providing%20social%20protection%20to%20our%20migrant%20construction%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECentrally%20sponsored%20schemes%20not%20audited%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20article%20titled%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fopinion%2Fcag-could-have-done-better%2Farticle67533089.ece%5C%22%3ECAG%20could%20have%20done%20better%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20Govind%20Bhattacharjee%20has%20pointed%20out%20that%20%E2%80%9Cexcept%20%5Bthe%5D%20PMAY%2C%20reports%20of%20which%20are%20available%20till%202022%2C%20and%20PM%20Kisan%2C%20%5Bthe%20performance%20audit%20of%20which%20is%5D%20understood%20to%20be%20underway%2C%20none%20of%20the%20other%20centrally%20sponsored%20schemes%20have%20been%20audited%20beyond%20the%20fiscal%20year%202018.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20hope%20that%20the%20next%20CAG%20would%20be%20able%20to%20sing%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20the%20executive%20that%20memorable%20stanza%20from%20Tagore%E2%80%99s%20poem%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3Echitto%20jethaay%20bhayshunyo%2C%20uccho%20jethaay%20shir%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cem%3Elekhaa%20pariksha%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5Baudit%5D%20%3Cem%3Ejethaay%20mukto%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOutstanding%20action%20taken%20notes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20audit%20paragraph%2C%20once%20finalised%20and%20figuring%20in%20an%20audit%20report%20that%20gets%20tabled%20in%20parliament%20or%20a%20legislative%20assembly%2C%20requires%20the%20audited%20entity%20to%20initiate%20corrective%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAudited%20entities%20are%20required%20to%20submit%20%E2%80%98action%20taken%20notes%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20CAG.%20Non-submission%20of%20such%20action%20taken%20notes%2C%20with%20delays%20running%20into%20years%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20augur%20well%20for%20audit%20findings%20leading%20to%20improved%20governance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20the%20conspicuous%20decision%20to%20not%20even%20report%20the%20number%20of%20outstanding%20action%20taken%20notes%20or%20audit%20paragraphs%20is%20a%20cause%20for%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fy5w51%2F4%2F%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22492%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYear-wise%20audit%20reports%20approved%20by%20the%20CAG%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fqft0m%2F3%2F%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22646%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Year-wise%20audit%20reports%20approved%20by%20the%20CAG%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22405%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fd92cfc90-273b-48c8-9fde-d6fe41cf7288%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHimanshu%20Upadhyaya%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0is%20at%20the%20School%20of%20Development%20Studies%2C%20Azim%20Premji%20University.%20Views%20are%20personal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705056325000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06163312%2FCAG-building-II.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcomptroller-auditor-general-review-2014-2023-india-black-boxed%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Some%20drawbacks%20of%20the%20CAG's%20performance%20during%20the%20last%20decade%20are%20an%20opaque%20selection%20process%2C%20slowed%20audits%20and%20unusual%20redactions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcomptroller-auditor-general-review-2014-2023-india-black-boxed%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22South%20Africa%20Is%20Taking%20Israel%20to%20Court%20for%20Genocide%20in%20Palestine.%20What%20Does%20It%20Mean%20for%20the%20War%20In%26nbsp%3BGaza%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08150335%2Fimage560x340cropped.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa%20has%20taken%20Israel%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icj-cij.org%2Fcase%2F192%5C%22%3EInternational%20Court%20of%20Justice%3C%2Fa%3E%20(ICJ%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20World%20Court)%20in%20The%20Hague%20claiming%20genocide%20has%20been%20committed%20against%20Palestinians%20during%20the%20Gaza%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20charge%20of%20genocide%20before%20the%20court%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20heated%20armed%20conflict%20is%20exceptional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20the%20significance%20of%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20claim%20against%20Israel%20has%20immense%20cultural%2C%20diplomatic%2C%20historical%2C%20and%20political%20significance.%20Israel%20has%20rejected%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20claim%20and%20vowed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67866342%5C%22%3Econtest%20the%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternational%20court%20cases%20such%20as%20these%20typically%20run%20for%20many%20years%20before%20a%20final%20judgement%20is%20reached%2C%20however%20South%20Africa%20has%20also%20requested%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icj-cij.org%2Fcase%2F192%2Fpress-releases%5C%22%3Eprovisional%20measures%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20a%20form%20of%20international%20injunction%20%E2%80%93%20and%20preliminary%20hearings%20will%20take%20place%20in%20The%20Hague%20on%20January%2011%20and%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20decision%20on%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20provisional%20measures%20request%20will%20most%20likely%20be%20made%20by%20the%20end%20of%20January%20with%20the%20potential%20to%20have%20a%20profound%20impact%20on%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20military%20campaign%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhich%20laws%20are%20in%20question%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fen%2Fgenocideprevention%2Fdocuments%2Fatrocity-crimes%2FDoc.1_Convention%2520on%2520the%2520Prevention%2520and%2520Punishment%2520of%2520the%2520Crime%2520of%2520Genocide.pdf%5C%22%3E1948%20Convention%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Prevention%20and%20Punishment%20of%20the%20Crime%20of%20Genocide%20(Genocide%20Convention)%20was%20adopted%20following%20the%201940s%20holocaust%20by%20the%20Nazi%20regime%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%20six%20million%20Jewish%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Genocide%20Convention%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20responses%20by%20the%20then%20fledgling%20United%20Nations%20to%20the%20holocaust.%20It%20was%20intended%20to%20clearly%20define%20genocide%2C%20prevent%20future%20genocides%2C%20and%20make%20nation%20states%20accountable%20for%20genocide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20total%20of%20153%20parties%20to%20the%20Genocide%20Convention%2C%20including%20Israel%20and%20South%20Africa%2C%20and%20it%20is%20widely%20seen%20as%20one%20of%20the%20pillars%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20human%20rights%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStates%20are%20accountable%20for%20genocide%20before%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%2C%20while%20individuals%20can%20be%20charged%20with%20the%20crime%20of%20genocide%20and%20placed%20on%20trial%20at%20the%20International%20Criminal%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGenocide%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2Fen%2Finstruments-mechanisms%2Finstruments%2Fconvention-prevention-and-punishment-crime-genocide%5C%22%3Edefined%20in%20the%20Convention%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20%E2%80%9Cacts%20committed%20with%20intent%20to%20destroy%2C%20in%20whole%20or%20in%20part%2C%20a%20national%2C%20ethnical%2C%20racial%20or%20religious%20group%E2%80%9D%20and%20extends%20to%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Ekilling%20members%20of%20the%20group%2C%20or%20causing%20serious%20bodily%20harm%20to%20members%20of%20the%20group%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Edeliberately%20inflicting%20on%20the%20group%20conditions%20of%20life%20calculated%20to%20bring%20about%20its%20physical%20destruction%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Eimposing%20measures%20to%20prevent%20births.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20case%20about%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20case%20against%20Israel%20under%20the%20Genocide%20Convention%20was%20commenced%20on%20December%2029%2C%202023%20following%20lodgement%20of%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icj-cij.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fcase-related%2F192%2F192-20231228-app-01-00-en.pdf%5C%22%3E84-page%20application%3C%2Fa%3E%20instituting%20the%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa%20has%20brought%20the%20case%20by%20relying%20on%20the%20principle%20that%20as%20a%20party%20to%20the%20Genocide%20Convention%2C%20it%20has%20an%20obligation%20to%20enforce%20legal%20rights%20owed%20to%20all%20people%20that%20genocide%20not%20be%20allowed.%20The%20claim%20could%20have%20been%20commenced%20by%20any%20other%20party%20to%20the%20convention%2C%20however%2C%20South%20Africa%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dirco.gov.za%2Fsouth-africa-calls-for-the-international-community-to-hold-israel-accountable-for-breaches-of-international-law%2F%5C%22%3Eraising%20concerns%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20genocide%20in%20Gaza%20since%20October%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20claim%20gives%20a%20historical%20context%20to%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20conduct%20in%20Palestine%2C%20recounts%20the%20Hamas%20terrorist%20attacks%20on%20October%207%2C%20and%20details%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20subsequent%20Gaza%20military%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParticular%20attention%20is%20given%20to%20the%20actions%20and%20conduct%20of%20Israeli%20political%20and%20military%20leaders%2C%20especially%20their%20statements%20as%20to%20how%20Israel%20intended%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20Hamas%20attacks%2C%20and%20the%20extent%20and%20scale%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20military%20operations%20and%20military%20objectives%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa%20then%20details%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20actual%20military%20conduct%20during%20the%20Gaza%20campaign%20and%20the%20consequences%20for%20Palestinian%20civilians.%20This%20conduct%20is%20linked%20directly%20back%20to%20acts%20of%20genocide%20as%20defined%20in%20the%20Genocide%20Convention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20court%20case%20takes%20two%20forms%3A%20a%20claim%20that%20Israel%20has%20committed%20genocide%20against%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%2C%20and%20the%20urgent%20request%20for%20provisional%20measures%20(international%20legal%20speak%20for%20expediting%20the%20process).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa%20has%20requested%20that%20the%20court%20order%20that%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20political%20and%20military%20leaders%2C%20and%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20military%2C%20immediately%20cease%20any%20activities%20that%20amount%20to%20an%20ongoing%20campaign%20of%20genocide%20against%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa%20will%20need%20to%20prove%2C%20both%20in%20law%20and%20in%20facts%2C%20that%20the%20case%20is%20admissible%2C%20that%20the%20World%20Court%20has%20jurisdiction%20to%20hear%20this%20claim%2C%20and%20that%20the%20application%20is%20urgent%2C%20requiring%20orders%20to%20prevent%20irreparable%20harm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImportantly%20at%20this%20stage%2C%20South%20Africa%20does%20not%20need%20to%20conclusively%20prove%20genocide%20has%20taken%20place.%20That%20comes%20at%20the%20later%20phase%2C%20called%20the%20Merits%20phase.%20South%20Africa%20does%2C%20however%2C%20need%20to%20demonstrate%20that%20Palestinians%20face%20irreparable%20harm%20and%20that%2C%20on%20the%20facts%2C%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20conduct%20could%20be%20considered%20to%20be%20acts%20of%20genocide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20will%20no%20doubt%20robustly%20resist%20any%20assertion%20genocide%20is%20occurring%20and%20argue%20its%20political%20and%20military%20leaders%20are%20acting%20consistently%20with%20international%20law%20in%20response%20to%20the%20threat%20posed%20by%20Hamas.%20Particular%20attention%20will%20probably%20be%20given%20to%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20right%20of%20self-defence%20following%20the%20October%207%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20cases%20like%20these%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20has%20been%20thrust%20into%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20not%20being%20asked%20to%20play%20the%20role%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council%20and%20settle%20that%20dispute.%20The%20court%E2%80%99s%20role%2C%20as%20a%20United%20Nations%20organ%2C%20is%20purely%20to%20apply%20the%20Genocide%20Convention%20and%20international%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%2C%20nevertheless%2C%20be%20acutely%20aware%20of%20the%20significance%20of%20its%20role%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20face%20of%20claims%20of%20an%20ongoing%20genocide.%20This%20has%20been%20reflected%20in%20how%20it%20has%20moved%20quickly%20to%20hear%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20potential%20outcomes%20from%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20provisional%20measures%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20may%20decline%20to%20order%20provisional%20measures.%20It%20may%2C%20for%20example%2C%20find%20it%20lacks%20jurisdiction%20and%20that%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20case%20is%20inadmissible%20on%20technical%20legal%20grounds%2C%20or%20the%20facts%20do%20not%20support%20the%20claims%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOr%20the%20court%20may%20uphold%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20request%20and%20order%20provisional%20measures.%20Any%20provisional%20measures%20ruling%20against%20Israel%20would%20require%20a%20radical%20modification%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20military%20operations%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20cannot%2C%20however%2C%20enforce%20its%20decisions.%20In%202022%2C%20for%20example%2C%20Russia%20ignored%20an%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2022%2Fmar%2F16%2Fun-international-court-of-justice-orders-russia-to-halt-invasion-of-ukraine%5C%22%3Eprovisional%20measures%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20its%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20what%20the%20court%20orders%2C%20Israel%20will%20retain%20its%20right%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jurist.org%2Fcommentary%2F2023%2F12%2F7-10-the-question-of-israels-right-to-self-defense-under-international-law%2F%5C%22%3Eself-defence%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20Hamas.%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Conversation%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcounter.theconversation.com%2Fcontent%2F220660%2Fcount.gif%3Fdistributor%3Drepublish-lightbox-basic%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fprofiles%2Fdonald-rothwell-9843%5C%22%3EDonald%20Rothwell%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Pro