20potential%20pitfalls%20of%20linking%20national%20identity%20solely%20with%20religious%20identity.%20While%20highlighting%20India%E2%80%99s%20historical%20Hindu%20roots%2C%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20government%20has%20been%20criticised%20for%20marginalising%20other%20religious%20and%20cultural%20groups.%20This%20tendency%20towards%20Hindu%20nationalism%20raises%20concerns%20about%20inclusivity%20and%20tolerance%2C%20core%20values%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Indian%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20attributing%20India%E2%80%99s%20success%20solely%20to%20its%20Hindu%20heritage%20risks%20erasing%20the%20contributions%20of%20other%20communities%20that%20have%20enriched%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20tapestry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffor-the-bjp-the-hindu-card-is-no-longer-as-potent-as-it-once-was%5C%22%3EFor%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20Hindu%20Card%20Is%20No%20Longer%20as%20Potent%20as%20It%20Once%20Was%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20rise%20of%20Hindu%20pride%20under%20Modi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20Hindu%20pride%20under%20Modi%20is%20also%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20global%20trend%20of%20identity%20politics%20and%20cultural%20assertiveness.%20From%20Brexit%20to%20the%20rise%20of%20right-wing%20populism%20in%20various%20countries%2C%20we%20see%20communities%20reaffirming%20their%20cultural%20distinctiveness.%20In%20this%20context%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20experience%20aligns%20with%20a%20larger%20political%20shift%20rather%20than%20being%20solely%20attributable%20to%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20a%20holistic%20understanding%20of%20Hindu%20pride%20goes%20beyond%20a%20singular%20political%20figure.%20It%E2%80%99s%20an%20intricate%20interplay%20of%20historical%20context%2C%20social%20anxieties%2C%20the%20yearning%20for%20global%20recognition%2C%20and%20the%20appeal%20of%20a%20confident%20leader%20promoting%20a%20revitalised%20national%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20narrative%20of%20Hindu%20pride%20in%20the%20post-Modi%20era%20is%2C%20therefore%2C%20not%20a%20simple%20one%20of%20unalloyed%20positivity%20or%20negativity.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20complex%20tapestry%20woven%20with%20threads%20of%20historical%20legacy%2C%20diasporic%20experiences%2C%20sociopolitical%20shifts%2C%20and%20the%20rise%20of%20a%20specific%20political%20ideology.%20To%20understand%20the%20nuances%20of%20Hindu%20pride%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20to%20move%20beyond%20simplistic%20cause-and-effect%20explanations%20and%20engage%20with%20the%20rich%20and%20complex%20history%20of%20Hindu%20identity%2C%20its%20diverse%20expressions%2C%20and%20its%20evolving%20role%20in%20contemporary%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20to%20acknowledge%20that%20Hindu%20pride%20is%20not%20monolithic.%20It%20manifests%20in%20various%20ways%2C%20from%20practicing%20yoga%20and%20celebrating%20festivals%20to%20advocating%20for%20social%20reforms%20within%20the%20Hindu%20community.%20NRIs%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20experience%20a%20unique%20blend%20of%20cultural%20influences%20and%20identities%2C%20leading%20to%20diverse%20expressions%20of%20Hindu%20pride%2C%20often%20characterised%20by%20a%20nuanced%20understanding%20of%20their%20heritage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20surge%20in%20Hindu%20pride%20reflects%20a%20positive%20affirmation%20of%20identity%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20essential%20to%20address%20the%20potential%20pitfalls.%20The%20association%20of%20Hindu%20identity%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20policies%20has%20led%20to%20concerns%20about%20Hindu%20nationalism%2C%20majoritarianism%2C%20and%20the%20marginalisation%20of%20other%20religious%20and%20cultural%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20forward%2C%20the%20challenge%20lies%20in%20ensuring%20that%20cultural%20pride%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20morph%20into%20exclusionary%20nationalism.%20India%E2%80%99s%20strength%20lies%20in%20its%20rich